## 5. Booster Fun Treatments and Collectible Card Categories

### 5.1 Borderless Scene Cards

- Scene cards combine to form larger Marvel artwork scenes.
- They can be collected for decks, binders, display, or gameplay.
- There are six scenes available from cards found in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters:
  - A 4-card Fantastic Four scene by Leinil Francis Yu and Sunny Gho.
  - A 4-card Daredevil vs. Hell’s Kitchen foes scene by Kev Walker.
  - A 6-card Captain America vs. HYDRA scene by Annie Wu.
  - A 6-card gamma-themed confrontation scene by Adi Granov.
  - An 18-card cosmic cube battle scene by Johan Grenier.
  - A 5-card meal-sharing scene by Chris Bachalo, formed from the front faces of double-sided scene cards.
- Scene cards in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters include:
  - 3 commons.
  - 12 uncommons.
  - 8 rares.
  - 15 mythic rares.
- Scene cards appear in non-foil and traditional foil in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.
- There are two Scene Boxes, and each Scene Box contains 6 traditional foil new-to-Magic borderless scene cards.
- Non-foil versions of Scene Box scene cards appear in Collector Boosters.

### 5.2 Borderless Lands

- The set introduces five new rare dual lands.
- Each rare dual land has a borderless version showing the location through an Avengers computer-screen style treatment.
- There are 5 rare borderless lands.
- They appear in non-foil and traditional foil versions in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.

### 5.3 Showcase Panel Cards

- Showcase panel cards use a comic-panel-inspired frame.
- They highlight major Marvel objects, stories, and moments.
- Examples include Mjölnir, Hammer of Thor and Armor Wars.
- There are 11 rare showcase panel cards and 6 mythic rare showcase panel cards.
- They appear in non-foil and traditional foil versions in Play Boosters and Collector Boosters.

### 5.4 Full-Art City Calm and City Chaos Basic Lands

The set includes two full-art basic land cycles:

- City calm basic lands: quieter moments featuring Super Heroes in calmer city settings.
- City chaos basic lands: action-focused city scenes across Marvel locations.

Availability by product:

| Product | Basic land treatment availability |
|---|---|
| Play Boosters | Non-foil and traditional foil city calm and city chaos basics |
| Collector Boosters | Traditional foil city calm and city chaos basics |
| Jumpstart Boosters | 1 non-foil city calm or city chaos basic per booster |
| Bundles | 1 non-foil and 1 traditional foil city chaos basic of each type |
| Gift Bundles | 1 non-foil and 1 traditional foil city calm basic of each type |
| Collector’s Edition Commander Decks | Surge foil city calm and city chaos basics |
| Beginner Boxes | Non-foil city calm and city chaos basics |

