## 6.2 Collector Boosters

A Collector Booster box contains 12 Collector Boosters.

Each Collector Booster contains:

- 15 Magic cards.
- 1 art card or traditional foil double-sided token.

### Collector Booster card slot structure

| Slot | Contents / notes |
|---|---|
| 3 traditional foil common cards | Main set commons and common dual lands. |
| 2 traditional foil uncommons | Main set uncommons. |
| 2 traditional foil common MSC cards | Jumpstart reprints or new-to-Magic Jumpstart cards. |
| 1 traditional foil uncommon MSC card | Mostly new-to-Magic Jumpstart cards, with some Jumpstart reprints. |
| 1 traditional foil common/uncommon scene card | Common or uncommon scene card. |
| 1 traditional foil city basic land | City calm or city chaos basic land. |
| 1 traditional foil rare/mythic card | Main set, scene, logo, Jumpstart, Welcome Deck, or related card category. |
| 1 non-foil Commander deck Booster Fun card | Extended-art rares/mythics or borderless face commanders. |
| 1 non-foil rare/mythic Booster Fun card | Extended art, scene, logo, panel, Scene Box card, borderless rare land, or source material card. |
| 1 source material card | Non-foil 75% or traditional foil 25%. |
| 1 foil Booster Fun rare/mythic card | Foil extended art, scene, logo, panel, borderless land, classic comic, Gauntlet Mind Stone, or ultra-limited cosmic foil Mind Stone. |
| 1 art card/token slot | Traditional foil double-sided token or art card. |

